title: Consensus Check: Community-Enabled Analytics via Yield-Generating Investment Strategies
body:
Should Uniswap governance grant $25M to fund Community-Enabled Analytics via a sustainable yield-generating investment strategy that:
1. Produces analytics that educate the community and drive growth
2. Allocates UNI to participants through bounties
3. Uses Uniswap’s own yield mechanisms to sustainably self-fund the program
